title: Will the Pixel 4a (Ohne SIM-Lock) work in Russia?
content: I want to order Pixel 4A from Germany to my Russian, but I am confused by the inscription on the official German version of the website Google Store - Pixel 4A (ohne SIM-Lock). Just on other sites, for example in the United States, it is written Unlocked. Tell me, please, the phone from Germany is unlocked for all Telecom operators?
